"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[include <a href=\"/component:scp-meta-title-hiding\">component:scp-meta-title-hiding</a> css-style=classic]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:start\">info:start</a>]]<br />\n**原文：**[http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4893 SCP-4893]<br />\n<br />\n**作者：**[[*user KoikeSanshouemon]]<br />\n<br />\n**譯者：**[[*user feitag]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:end\">info:end</a>]]<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n.footnotes-footer {<br />\ndisplay:none;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n#u-aaa ~ .after,<br />\n#u-aaa ~ * .after,<br />\n#u-aaa:target ~ .before,<br />\n#u-aaa:target ~ * .before{<br />\ndisplay: none;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n#u-aaa ~ .before,<br />\n#u-aaa ~ * .before,<br />\n#u-aaa:target ~ .after,<br />\n#u-aaa:target ~ * .after{<br />\ndisplay: inline;<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div id=&quot;u-aaa&quot; style=&quot;display: none;&quot;]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n**項目編號：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「迷信」「敵意」[[/footnote]][[/span]]-4893<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]項目等級[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lily_yellow width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「謊言」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rhododendron width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「危險」「警告」「小 心」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Gladiolus width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「力量」[[/footnote]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]Safe[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Begonia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「危險」[[/footnote]][[/span]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]特殊收容措施[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lily_yellow width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Odontoglossum width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「你是特別的」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「我是你的囚徒」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「保護」[[/footnote]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 應保存在 Site-630 內的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]標準項目儲物櫃[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fern width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「信賴和庇護處」[[/footnote]][[/span]]。禁止[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]查看[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「看著我」[[/footnote]][[/span]] [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]內容[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「訊息」[[/footnote]][[/span]]。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]描述[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lily_yellow width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Solidaster width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「豐富的知識」[[/footnote]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 是一本用[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]荷蘭語[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Tulip_orange width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]荷蘭的國花[[/footnote]][[/span]]寫成的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]詩集[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Amaryllis width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「田園詩」[[/footnote]][[/span]]，會導致讀者出現[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]聯覺[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_lavender width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「enchantment（著迷／附魔）」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lupine width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「想像」[[/footnote]][[/span]]，當受到[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]書面詞語[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]刺激時，會產生近義花語的花朵之幻象。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 在[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]] 1550 年[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fir width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「時間」[[/footnote]][[/span]]被[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]發現[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]，當時位於[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]荷蘭馬斯垂克[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Tulip width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Tulip_orange width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]郊外的村莊發現了一本開花的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]書[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Amaryllis width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的傳言引起了[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]基金會[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「我克服困難」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「智慧」[[/footnote]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「良好的教育」[[/footnote]][[/span]]的興趣。因為[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]記憶消除[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Pansy width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「回憶」[[/footnote]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Poppy width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「遺忘」[[/footnote]][[/span]]已證明無效，所以 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 與其[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]前任[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Cyclamen width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「辭職與告別」[[/footnote]][[/span]]持有者以及其他 ██ 名受曝個體一起被[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]收容[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]，受曝個體被編號為 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1。截至 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]1613 年[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fir width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]] [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]12 月[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Narcissus width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]12 月的誕生花[[/footnote]][[/span]] 9 日，所有 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1 的實例都[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]死亡[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lily width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「死亡」[[/footnote]][[/span]]了。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n[[size larger]]**需要 3 級或更高[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]安保權限[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_white width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「保密與沉默」[[/footnote]][[/span]]。認證中...**[[/size]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n[[size larger]]**身分認證完成。存取 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-KM2 檔案。**[[/size]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n@@@@<br />\n[[collapsible show=&quot;+ 開啟 SCP-4893-KM2 檔案&quot; hide=&quot;- 關閉 SCP-4893-KM2 檔案&quot;]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**項目編號：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]][[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/OrientalBittersweet width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「真實」[[/footnote]][[/span]][[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]項目等級[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rhododendron width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Gladiolus width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]Euclid[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Oleander width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「警慎」「小心」[[/footnote]][[/span]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]特殊收容措施[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/OrientalBittersweet width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Odontoglossum width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A 應位於 Site-630 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]標準人形收容間[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fern width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]或受到[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]基金會[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]管轄的宿舍單人房之中。不得給予任何可使 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A 書寫[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]文字[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的設備 (手寫、打字等等)。 和 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A 的所有溝通只可藉由錄音進行。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n自 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]1960 年[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fir width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]開始，[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A 在左鎖骨的皮下組織中，應安裝配有 GPS 與生命跡象偵測功能的微晶片。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]描述[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/OrientalBittersweet width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Solidaster width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]：**[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 是一種人形個體，[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 所寫下的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]文字[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]會導致讀者出現[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]聯覺[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_lavender width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Lupine width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]，將產生近義花語的花朵之幻象。[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]看見[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]] [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 所寫下之[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]文字[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的人，將會獲得與 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 相同的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]異常性[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_blue width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「神秘」[[/footnote]][[/span]] ([[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A)。<br />\n@@　@@<br />\n&nbsp;[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]1550 年[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fir width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]，[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 和一本[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]異常[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_blue width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]][[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]詩集[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Amaryllis width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]] ([[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1) 一同被發現，當時位於[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]荷蘭馬斯垂克[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Tulip width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Tulip_orange width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]郊外的村莊[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]發現[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]了一本開花的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]書[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Amaryllis width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的傳言引起了[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]基金會[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的興趣。[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]基金會[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]最初將 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]視為[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]][[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]異常現象[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_blue width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的起因，但 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1 的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]前任[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Cyclamen width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「辭職與告別」[[/footnote]][[/span]]持有者 ([[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A-1) 供認他創造了 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-1。結果因此發現 SCP-4893-A-1 是 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]異常現象[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Rose_blue width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]的主因。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n當個體[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]閱讀[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]&nbsp;&nbsp;[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 的一段實例時，他們會變成 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A，該個體的寫作會得到 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893 的性質，[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]直到其死亡[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Laurel_leaf width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「至死不渝」[[/footnote]][[/span]]。在 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]1758 年[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fir width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]以前，[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]D 級人員[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hyssop width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「犧牲」[[/footnote]][[/span]] 暴露於 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893，以保持至少存在一名現存的 [[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]SCP[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]-4893-A，但反覆的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]收容[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]突破導致改用現在的[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]]收容措施[[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[/span]]。<br />\n[[/collapsible]]<br />\n[[span class=&quot;before&quot;]][#u-aaa + 僅供 SCP-4893 負責研究員親眼查看][[/span]][[span class=&quot;after&quot;]][#no-link - 至我的繼任者][[/span]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;after&quot;]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n@@@@<br />\n首先，[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CasaBlanca width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「慶祝」[[/footnote]]升遷。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n從今天起，你是[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 的[[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Burdock width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「強求」[[/footnote]]研究員，並因此是 [[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 本身。對你來說[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]此則[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]會非常困難， 但你很快就會習慣。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n好吧，你可能在好奇。為什麼我必須要變成 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893？為什麼不用[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hyssop width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]？<br />\n@@@@<br />\n一開始當 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 被[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sanvitalia width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]時是如此沒錯。事實上，[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 曾&nbsp;&nbsp;[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Alstroemeria width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「持續」[[/footnote]] 了好多年都是 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Goldenrod width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「健康」[[/footnote]]、年輕的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hyssop width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]。但今日有件事情變得不一樣了：識字率。今日在[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/JapaneseQuince width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「先鋒」[[/footnote]]以及[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Thoroughwort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「落後」[[/footnote]]國家的許多人都能讀寫 [[image <br />\nhttp://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]。不可避免地，暴露於 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/KamchatkaLily width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「詛咒」[[/footnote]]之可能性增加了。任何由[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 寫下或打出的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]] 都是感染源。有一些案例是過去曾[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Alstroemeria width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]] [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hyssop width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]在牆上刻下[[image&nbsp;&nbsp;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Iris width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]導致許多[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/GiantButterbur width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「同伴」[[/footnote]] 變成 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893。<br />\n@@@@<br />\n我們的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hollyhock width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「志向」[[/footnote]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Monkshood width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「騎士精神」[[/footnote]] 是「 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fern width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]、[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]、[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]」。僅僅是[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Fern width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]與[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]] 任何[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]並不夠好。因此最佳的方法是從能理解[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]的[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Hollyhock width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Monkshood width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]之[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Mistletoe width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Sage width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/CherryBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]人員中選擇[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 的 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Alstroemeria width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]來執行此任務。[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Alstroemeria width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]我們[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/PeachBlossom width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]與[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Geranium_red width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]的項目。然後，有一天你會[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Alstroemeria width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Shephherd'sPurse width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「我給你我的全部」[[/footnote]]這個[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Clover_white width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「誓言」[[/footnote]]給另外某個人。[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Carnation_white width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]][[footnote]]「好運」[[/footnote]]<br />\n@@@@<br />\n[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Cyclamen width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]] [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/StJhonswort width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]]-4893 [[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4893/Burdock width=&quot;24&quot; hight=&quot;24&quot;]] 研究員<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[footnoteblock]]<br />\n[[div class=&quot;footer-wikiwalk-nav&quot;]]<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n&lt;&lt; [[[SCP-4892]]] | SCP-4893 | [[[SCP-4894]]] &gt;&gt;<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n[[/div]]\n</div>\n"